WEBVTT

00:02.001 --> 00:03.046
Previously onMom...

00:03.133 --> 00:04.003
So, Regina,
tell us about you.

00:04.091 --> 00:06.658
I'm a money manager.

00:06.745 --> 00:07.920
People trust me
with millions of dollars.

00:08.007 --> 00:10.445
So, yeah,

00:10.532 --> 00:13.796
maybe I like to take the edge
off at the end of the day

00:13.883 --> 00:16.451
with a couple bottles of wine.

00:16.538 --> 00:18.931
Few shots of tequila.

00:19.019 --> 00:20.759
Fistful of muscle relaxers.

00:22.283 --> 00:25.373
I'm dating this sweet, smart,

00:25.460 --> 00:29.725
smokin' hot guy
who's just a train wreck.

00:31.509 --> 00:32.075
Can I ask you something?

00:32.162 --> 00:34.338
Sure.

00:34.425 --> 00:36.775
Are sober people
allowed to do coke?

00:38.995 --> 00:41.432
You know how I told you people
trust me with their money?

00:41.519 --> 00:42.477
Yeah.

00:42.564 --> 00:44.044
They shouldn't.

00:45.219 --> 00:46.872
I embezzled from my clients.

00:46.959 --> 00:49.658
Why?

00:49.745 --> 00:51.399
What kind of
question is that?

00:51.486 --> 00:52.617
What's a better question?

00:52.704 --> 00:54.880
How?

00:54.967 --> 00:56.708
Anyway...

00:56.795 --> 01:00.582
The real reason I came here
tonight was...

01:00.669 --> 01:03.846
I think the police might be
waiting for me at my house.

01:05.500 --> 01:08.198
I can't believe
they found you guilty.

01:08.285 --> 01:10.070
I can. I stole $3 million.

01:12.376 --> 01:14.596
Kind of gives you faith
in the legal system.

01:14.683 --> 01:15.249
[laughs]

01:15.336 --> 01:17.860
Shut up.

01:17.947 --> 01:20.645
So what
happens next?

01:20.732 --> 01:22.169
There's a sentencing hearing.

01:22.256 --> 01:24.084
I'm hoping the judge
will go easy on me

01:24.171 --> 01:25.781
'cause I've been
turning my life around.

01:25.868 --> 01:27.174
Have you?Don't push me, Chopstick.

01:30.438 --> 01:31.613
Maybe they'll send you
to one of those

01:31.700 --> 01:33.093
swanky
country club jails.

01:33.180 --> 01:35.791
Get real. I'm a black woman

01:35.878 --> 01:37.575
who embezzled money
from white people.

01:37.662 --> 01:39.925
I'm going to jailjail.

01:40.012 --> 01:41.971
Someone's gonna buy my ass
for a Kit Kat bar.

01:42.058 --> 01:44.495
Well, it's only fair.

01:44.582 --> 01:47.846
Kit Kat bars helped
build that thing.

01:47.933 --> 01:51.023
My lawyer said it might help if
I had some character witnesses.

01:51.111 --> 01:53.287
Oh, so you need people
who can testify to how you've

01:53.374 --> 01:55.463
turned into a productive
member of society.

01:55.550 --> 01:58.422
Yeah.Yikes.

01:58.509 --> 02:02.339
Well, it wouldn't be the first
time I've lied under oath.

02:02.426 --> 02:04.167
Thanks, but I was kind of hoping
for someone a little less...

02:04.254 --> 02:06.561
sketchy.

02:06.648 --> 02:10.042
That's funny.
Sketchy was my street name.

02:10.130 --> 02:11.696
What about you, Christy?

02:11.783 --> 02:14.569
Oh, I'm not
squeaky clean, either.

02:14.656 --> 02:16.179
Especially not in Nevada.

02:16.266 --> 02:18.790
And parts of Utah.

02:18.877 --> 02:20.183
I'm not allowed
to travel abroad.

02:20.270 --> 02:23.621
It's not
a competition, Mom.

02:23.708 --> 02:25.623
You'll
be great.

02:25.710 --> 02:28.235
Just look at the judge like one
of those big-eyed kid paintings.

02:28.322 --> 02:29.410
He'll eat it up.

02:29.497 --> 02:31.151
You think?Oh. Show me.

02:33.153 --> 02:36.547
Open your mouth a little, so you
look like you're about to cry.

02:39.115 --> 02:42.423
Tell me that doesn't look
like house arrest to you.

02:43.641 --> 02:46.166
Come on, I can do that.

02:50.300 --> 02:54.435
You look like someone
who just huffed some paint.

02:54.522 --> 02:55.784
Okay, for that,
you're buying.

02:55.871 --> 02:57.177
Mom. She's
going to prison.

02:57.264 --> 02:58.656
Where she will eat for free.

02:58.743 --> 03:01.050
Come on, we're gonna
be late for the meeting.

03:01.137 --> 03:04.096
Oh, actually,
I can't make it.

03:04.184 --> 03:05.620
I've got to help
a friend move.

03:05.707 --> 03:06.621
Who's the friend?

03:06.708 --> 03:07.752
Do you know Denise?

03:07.839 --> 03:08.840
