She's going to see

03:21.592 --> 03:22.071
her pothead boyfriend.

03:22.158 --> 03:24.552
Wow.

03:24.639 --> 03:26.336
All I saw was the big eyes.

03:26.423 --> 03:28.164
She's gonna be great
on the stand.

03:28.251 --> 03:30.297
You ready to go?

03:30.384 --> 03:33.256
Let me just use
the ladies' room.

03:33.343 --> 03:34.692
Why don't you just take a leak

03:34.779 --> 03:35.345
right here
in front of everybody?

03:35.432 --> 03:37.913
