04:19.519 --> 04:23.828
I think I'm falling
in love with you.

04:23.915 --> 04:26.440
Oh.

04:26.527 --> 04:29.530
You freaked out?

04:29.617 --> 04:30.922
That depends.

04:31.009 --> 04:33.142
How high are you right now?

04:33.229 --> 04:36.188
On a scale of Woody Harrelson
to Willie Nelson.

04:37.494 --> 04:39.322
Snoop Dogg.

04:39.409 --> 04:41.411
So you might not
remember this.

04:41.498 --> 04:44.022
I'll remember.

04:45.720 --> 04:48.113
