04:53.467 --> 04:55.338
I might be.

04:55.425 --> 04:57.297
Good.

04:57.384 --> 04:59.821
[soft laugh]

05:01.997 --> 05:03.215
Mmm.Mmm.

05:03.303 --> 05:04.695
You ready for round two?

05:04.782 --> 05:06.131
Mm. I am.

05:06.218 --> 05:07.655
