05:30.504 --> 05:31.548
[husky voice]:
Gabriel.

05:31.635 --> 05:34.116
It's Christy.

05:34.203 --> 05:36.423
I-I think I got that thing
that's going around.

05:36.510 --> 05:39.991
So I won't be in today,
maybe tomorrow. Bye.

05:41.036 --> 05:42.820
