that up for you?

06:39.877 --> 06:41.836
Fine.

06:45.013 --> 06:45.622
So, a long night, huh?

06:45.709 --> 06:48.538
Ugh, brutal.

06:48.625 --> 06:51.106
I'm really thinking
about going back to school.

06:51.193 --> 06:53.282
