mean on your back?

07:03.205 --> 07:04.902
What?

07:04.989 --> 07:07.252
Gabriel called to say
he's sorry you missed work

07:07.339 --> 07:09.341
and hopes you're feeling better.

07:14.782 --> 07:18.046
So what are you thinking
about studying in school?

07:20.004 --> 07:20.744
[sighs]

07:20.831 --> 07:22.920
All right, fine.

07:23.007 --> 07:25.009
I blew off work
and spent the night with David.

07:25.096 --> 07:26.533
But why lie about it?

07:26.620 --> 07:29.057
'Cause I'm kind of a liar.

07:32.495 --> 07:34.062
Is that where you were
when you missed

07:34.149 --> 07:35.672
