07:50.295 --> 07:52.297
You are the best grandmother.

07:52.384 --> 07:56.519
Yeah, only because
you're the worst mother.

07:56.606 --> 07:58.739
Look, I am not gonna tell you
how to live your life,

07:58.826 --> 08:00.741
