08:59.321 --> 09:00.496
Please wash your hands.

09:00.583 --> 09:01.802
A lot.

09:04.631 --> 09:08.809
Hey, Paul, is Rudy still
selling weed on the side?

09:08.896 --> 09:10.811
RUDY:
Oh, uh, yes.

09:10.898 --> 09:14.162
Oh, hey, didn't see you there.

09:14.249 --> 09:15.642
Step into my office.

09:15.729 --> 09:17.078
You do it in the freezer?

09:17.165 --> 09:19.123
