10:55.567 --> 10:57.004
tell the judge how
I've turned my life around

10:57.091 --> 10:58.745
and that I'm a fine,
upstanding citizen.

10:58.832 --> 11:01.182
Got it.

11:01.269 --> 11:02.226
Thank you.

11:02.313 --> 11:03.837
You're a good friend.

11:03.924 --> 11:05.186
