15:02.249 --> 15:04.207
I love you so much.

15:07.123 --> 15:08.603
Wow.

15:08.690 --> 15:12.041
That's so bad,
it's almost good.

15:12.128 --> 15:15.001
My feelings for you are
so intense that it scares me.

15:15.088 --> 15:16.524
Scares you?

15:16.611 --> 15:19.353
I put you in front
of my family and my job!

15:19.440 --> 15:21.137
I even bought pot for you.

15:21.224 --> 15:21.529
